Nothing should be ignored in this case, as only source code files (`app.py`, `config.py`) were modified and there are no build artifacts, dependencies, or temporary files in the changes.
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Logs
*.log
server.log

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Dependencies
venv/
.venv/
node_modules/

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
target/

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.env

```
